      <title>内塔尼亚胡呼吁以色列控制加沙食品分配</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/netanyahu-calls-for-israeli-control-over-gaza-food-distribution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡周三表示，以色列计划从哈马斯手中夺取对加沙地带粮食分配的控制权，他称此举是为了阻止哈马斯霸占人道主义援助物资的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/netanyahu-calls-for-israeli-control-over-gaza-food-distribution</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:48:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将推动资本利得税率降至 39.6% 以下，与拜登唱反调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/harris-to-push-capital-gains-tax-rate-below-39-6-bucking-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位竞选官员透露，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯正计划削减总统乔·拜登提出的资本利得税增加幅度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/harris-to-push-capital-gains-tax-rate-below-39-6-bucking-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织敦促南非新政府实施大胆改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/imf-urges-new-south-african-government-to-implement-bold-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，南非新多党政府应实施大胆改革，以充分发挥经济潜力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/imf-urges-new-south-african-government-to-implement-bold-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:12:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将阻止新日铁收购美国钢铁公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/biden-to-block-nippon-steel-us-steel-deal-washington-post-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国总统拜登正准备阻止新日本制铁公司以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/biden-to-block-nippon-steel-us-steel-deal-washington-post-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:59:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基将在改组中提名西比哈为乌克兰外交部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/zelenskiy-to-nominate-sybiha-as-foreign-minister-in-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基将提名高级外交官、前驻土耳其大使安德烈·西比哈 (Andrii Sybiha) 担任外交部长，这是自 2022 年俄罗斯入侵以来最大规模内阁改组的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/zelenskiy-to-nominate-sybiha-as-foreign-minister-in-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:49:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国指责俄罗斯支持的实体干预 2024 年选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-accuses-russian-backed-entities-of-2024-election-meddling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府周三宣布了一系列行动，旨在阻止据称由俄罗斯支持的干预 2024 年大选的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-accuses-russian-backed-entities-of-2024-election-meddling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新民主党终止权力分享协议，特鲁多政府失去关键盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/canada-s-ndp-pulls-out-of-deal-propping-up-trudeau-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[让加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的自由党继续执政的议会协议于周三破裂，增加了提前举行大选的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/canada-s-ndp-pulls-out-of-deal-propping-up-trudeau-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:54:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙选择埃斯克里瓦部长领导央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/spain-picks-minister-jose-luis-escriva-to-lead-the-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府部长何塞·路易斯·埃斯克里瓦 (Jose Luis Escriva) 被选为该国央行行长，以参与欧元区下周可能做出的降息决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/spain-picks-minister-jose-luis-escriva-to-lead-the-central-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 13:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰准备应对国际货币基金组织要求其货币贬值和降息的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ukraine-braces-for-imf-pressure-to-devalue-currency-cut-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，乌克兰官员准备本周向国际货币基金组织施压，要求其加快货币贬值、降低利率并加大增税力度，以填补该国的预算缺口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ukraine-braces-for-imf-pressure-to-devalue-currency-cut-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 07:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国移民法庭不注重正义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/us-immigration-court-system-falls-to-politics-failing-asylum-seekers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[决定庇护案件的系统正在失败，这不仅仅是因为它不堪重负。必须采取一些大胆的措施来修复一个从本质上就有缺陷的程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/us-immigration-court-system-falls-to-politics-failing-asylum-seekers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
